608-642 Henry Street, west side, between Coles and Rapelyea Streets. A view of the Norwegian Lutheran Church, and to the right P.S. No. 142. No. 606, partly visible at the extreme right, is north of Rapelyea Street.
About 1928.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
